Author: Azaryxe
Text: As difficult as it is, try and open upto your bf so he can help support you through the meal. I can assure you won't be annoying him in the slightest, if anything, he'll be glad you felt comfortable enough to be vulnerable. Any weight you gain will be as a result of the food being in you, it won't immediately become fat. In fact, you likely won't gain any lasting weight.  Try and push through and eat the breakfast, but don't force yourself if it becomes too overwhelming. Everything will be okay, I promise.
